{
  "texts": [
    "Consequently, the ability to utilize these advanced AI tools will profoundly influence social mobility.",
    "Against this backdrop of rapid generative AI and AGI advancements, coupled with emerging paid subscription models and signs of a widening digital divide in the AI era, this paper researches three questions: 1.",
    "What's the meaning of \"AI for All\", what's the theoretical foundation of it? 2.",
    "Is the current situationcharacterized mainly by soft-law declarations advocating \"AI for All\"sufficient? 3.",
    "How can we establish legal protections for the principle of \"AI for All,\" effectively integrating soft and hard laws to bridge the gap between innovation and development?"
  ]
}